               <orth>earball</orth>
            </form>
            <def>tail.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="AOHenley_GlasgowDJMacVicarlobster-idp109768424">
            <form>
               <orth>buigneag</orth>
            </form>
            <def>a lobster found in crevices near the shore after casting its shell in summertime.</def>
         </entry>
         <head
             xml:id="AOHenley_GlasgowDJMacVicarlobster-d0e108"
            >The Creel</head>
